1
00:00:38,140 --> 00:00:40,660
♪The blade dance
causing ripples to spread across the lake♪

2
00:00:40,660 --> 00:00:43,620
♪Waving the banner amidst the storm and rain♪

3
00:00:44,260 --> 00:00:46,900
♪The snow is not bothered
by the sadness and the happiness♪

4
00:00:46,900 --> 00:00:49,620
♪Blazing through the desert
with the rein in hands♪

5
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:52,820
♪Young and inexperienced, it is apparent♪

6
00:00:53,140 --> 00:00:55,700
♪Bold ambition
interspersed with recklessness♪

7
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:58,900
♪Mind not the predestination♪

8
00:00:58,900 --> 00:01:01,940
♪Solving all the problems
that fate presents me♪

9
00:01:01,940 --> 00:01:03,420
♪From all the trials and hardship♪

10
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:05,180
♪Spawn the vast courage♪

11
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:06,900
♪The journey to seek glory and justice♪

12
00:01:06,900 --> 00:01:08,500
♪Is not in vain♪

13
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:10,220
♪One smile is all it takes
to get what you're thinking♪

14
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:13,540
♪A ballad to our journey♪

15
00:01:14,900 --> 00:01:18,020
♪Pursuing the dream of our youth♪

16
00:01:18,020 --> 00:01:20,980
♪We take everything as it comes♪

17
00:01:21,180 --> 00:01:24,180
♪The distant land might be dangerous♪

18
00:01:24,180 --> 00:01:27,020
♪But what's life without an adventure?♪

19
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:30,100
♪Youths are supposed to dream big and be sharp♪

20
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:33,420
♪Every struggle in life has taught us♪

21
00:01:33,420 --> 00:01:35,380
♪That we shall do what we can wherever we go♪

22
00:01:35,380 --> 00:01:40,900
♪Together, another journey awaits♪

23
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:50,020
[The Blood of Youth]

24
00:01:50,250 --> 00:01:52,970
[Episode 4]

25
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:00,660
Any news of that person?

26
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:02,460
No.

27
00:02:03,420 --> 00:02:04,700
It was chaotic last night.

28
00:02:05,380 --> 00:02:06,580
As we were pursuing them,

29
00:02:06,940 --> 00:02:07,580
we even clashed

30
00:02:07,700 --> 00:02:08,460
with several groups of scouts.

31
00:02:09,780 --> 00:02:10,380
We ended up...

32
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:13,220
He deliberately leaked his whereabouts

33
00:02:14,100 --> 00:02:15,540
to lure us

34
00:02:16,210 --> 00:02:17,460
and find our camp

35
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:18,860
by following the clues he found.

36
00:02:19,580 --> 00:02:20,980
After that, he caused chaos

37
00:02:21,020 --> 00:02:21,980
by surprise

38
00:02:22,380 --> 00:02:23,580
and escaped.

39
00:02:24,820 --> 00:02:26,220
Then he used us

40
00:02:26,580 --> 00:02:28,860
to help him get rid of those following him.

41
00:02:29,540 --> 00:02:30,700
Wuxin

42
00:02:32,180 --> 00:02:33,940
sure came up with a great plot.

43
00:02:35,540 --> 00:02:37,700
Unless we get a sword deity to make a move,

44
00:02:38,460 --> 00:02:41,700
or else it'll be difficult to find him again.

45
00:02:42,100 --> 00:02:43,660
Mister, should we ask...

46
00:02:45,260 --> 00:02:47,140
We don't need to alert my father about this.

47
00:02:48,580 --> 00:02:52,260
Besides, I can guess

48
00:02:52,980 --> 00:02:54,580
where he's heading.

49
00:03:04,740 --> 00:03:05,340
Anyone here?

50
00:03:07,740 --> 00:03:08,380
Is there anyone around?

51
00:03:09,380 --> 00:03:10,980
Are you still going to deny that we're lost?

52
00:03:11,500 --> 00:03:12,540
This is clearly

53
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:13,340
an inn in Beili.

54
00:03:14,780 --> 00:03:16,210
We went the opposite way.

55
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:19,460
We may have taken the wrong road.

56
00:03:20,060 --> 00:03:21,460
But the direction is right.

57
00:03:22,180 --> 00:03:23,100
We were heading in the west direction.

58
00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:24,620
So how can we get lost?

59
00:03:41,860 --> 00:03:42,500
(What's this?)

60
00:03:44,820 --> 00:03:45,500
(Master?)

61
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:08,500
[The Sixth Prince, Xiao Chuhe,
shall be removed from the family registry]

62
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:09,380
[and demoted to commoner.
He shall leave the capital city immediately]

63
00:04:09,380 --> 00:04:09,860
[and not return unless summoned.]

64
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:29,780
Look how heavily at it rains!

65
00:04:29,980 --> 00:04:30,900
How strange it is.

66
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:47,420
Who's there?

67
00:05:20,820 --> 00:05:21,540
Who are you?

68
00:05:22,940 --> 00:05:23,940
Someone who's here to kill you.

69
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:53,540
I heard you've already reached
the Insouciant Phase

70
00:05:53,980 --> 00:05:56,180
at a young age.

71
00:05:56,980 --> 00:05:58,140
It looks to be true.

72
00:05:59,540 --> 00:06:00,820
It's a pity

73
00:06:02,060 --> 00:06:03,460
if you have to die like this.

74
00:07:27,860 --> 00:07:28,380
Xiao Se.

75
00:07:30,300 --> 00:07:31,060
This place is too dilapidated.

76
00:07:31,300 --> 00:07:32,460
We can't stay here at all.

77
00:07:33,700 --> 00:07:34,740
It'll be dark soon.

78
00:07:35,340 --> 00:07:36,020
Why don't we

79
00:07:36,340 --> 00:07:36,940
spend the night here

80
00:07:37,220 --> 00:07:37,900
after cleaning this place up a bit?

81
00:07:39,980 --> 00:07:41,260
Didn't you just tell me

82
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:42,740
we should get back on the road

83
00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:44,140
because it's not normal

84
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:45,180
for an inn to appear out of a sudden?

85
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:46,260
I've changed my mind.

86
00:07:48,460 --> 00:07:49,340
Xiao Se, what do you think?

87
00:07:50,980 --> 00:07:51,620
I'm fine with it.

88
00:08:40,180 --> 00:08:41,420
I knew you weren't asleep.

89
00:08:42,140 --> 00:08:43,460
The mark was left

90
00:08:43,700 --> 00:08:45,140
by Polymath of the martial arts world, right?

91
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:48,260
You're his disciple?

92
00:08:49,700 --> 00:08:50,340
You can say that.

93
00:08:52,900 --> 00:08:53,660
No wonder you know

94
00:08:53,860 --> 00:08:55,060
so many things about the martial arts world.

95
00:08:56,740 --> 00:08:57,660
Old Wangyou

96
00:08:57,860 --> 00:08:59,020
once told me

97
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:00,540
that Polymath

98
00:09:00,900 --> 00:09:02,340
has a disciple by the last name Xiao.

99
00:09:03,780 --> 00:09:05,540
You should mind your own business.

100
00:09:08,060 --> 00:09:08,860
I should say

101
00:09:09,260 --> 00:09:10,420
the same to you.

102
00:09:11,620 --> 00:09:11,980
Mr. Xiao,

103
00:09:12,900 --> 00:09:15,260
remember to come back before the day breaks.

104
00:09:19,180 --> 00:09:20,260
You really hold a grudge.

105
00:09:36,300 --> 00:09:36,860
Master.

106
00:09:37,860 --> 00:09:39,860
[Ji Ruofeng, Polymath]

107
00:09:48,180 --> 00:09:50,220
Are you heading to Xueyue City?

108
00:09:52,260 --> 00:09:52,620
Yes.

109
00:09:53,780 --> 00:09:54,860
Do you know

110
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:56,780
the consequences

111
00:09:57,180 --> 00:09:58,260
if you enter Xueyue City?

112
00:10:00,460 --> 00:10:01,300
I heard

113
00:10:03,300 --> 00:10:05,340
you are doing it for 500 silver taels.

114
00:10:07,820 --> 00:10:10,060
Master, you're indeed worthy
to be called Polymath.

115
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:11,580
You actually found out.

116
00:10:13,180 --> 00:10:15,100
Is it all because of 500 silver taels?

117
00:10:16,180 --> 00:10:17,580
Anything related to silver taels

118
00:10:17,580 --> 00:10:18,500
is important, after all.

119
00:10:19,460 --> 00:10:21,740
All right, it's for 500 silver taels.

120
00:10:22,940 --> 00:10:24,980
But it's not a small amount.

121
00:10:25,460 --> 00:10:28,420
Can Xueyue City afford it?

122
00:10:29,100 --> 00:10:30,220
They can't.

123
00:10:31,980 --> 00:10:33,100
But I'm certain

124
00:10:33,740 --> 00:10:34,820
they'd be happy

125
00:10:34,980 --> 00:10:36,580
to help me claim the money.

126
00:10:37,060 --> 00:10:39,100
Yes, they'd be happy indeed.

127
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:40,500
Not only they would,

128
00:10:40,700 --> 00:10:42,700
any major force in the martial arts world

129
00:10:42,860 --> 00:10:44,220
would be happy

130
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:45,820
to claim the 500 silver taels for you.

131
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:47,460
However...

132
00:10:47,700 --> 00:10:48,460
However,

133
00:10:50,060 --> 00:10:51,500
I'm not the only person

134
00:10:51,580 --> 00:10:52,580
who can claim this money.

135
00:10:54,220 --> 00:10:54,620
I know that.

136
00:10:56,460 --> 00:10:58,740
You're the least advantaged one.

137
00:10:59,260 --> 00:11:00,460
We need to fight

138
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:02,740
for some things.

139
00:11:03,580 --> 00:11:04,220
If I don't try it,

140
00:11:04,220 --> 00:11:05,700
how will I know the outcome?

141
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:07,860
If you fail,

142
00:11:09,700 --> 00:11:10,980
you'll die.

143
00:11:12,580 --> 00:11:14,180
I've died once,

144
00:11:15,180 --> 00:11:15,820
haven't I?

145
00:11:16,180 --> 00:11:17,340
Even the Sword Deity failed

146
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:18,220
to kill me.

147
00:11:18,460 --> 00:11:19,700
Stop probing.

148
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:22,300
I already know

149
00:11:22,500 --> 00:11:24,580
who crippled your martial arts

150
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:28,220
and seriously injured me that night.

151
00:11:31,500 --> 00:11:33,700
Was it the Wrathful Sword Deity, Yan Zhantian?

152
00:11:36,100 --> 00:11:38,180
Could it be the Lone Sword Deity, Luo Qingyang?

153
00:11:39,580 --> 00:11:40,500
Stop guessing.

154
00:11:41,060 --> 00:11:43,420
Since you've decided to let go,

155
00:11:43,980 --> 00:11:45,580
stop trying to find out.

156
00:11:47,980 --> 00:11:49,580
It's only 500 silver taels, isn't it?

157
00:11:50,340 --> 00:11:51,660
If you compare it to life,

158
00:11:52,460 --> 00:11:53,740
you should know

159
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:57,060
which one is more important.

160
00:12:01,860 --> 00:12:02,820
It looks like

161
00:12:03,100 --> 00:12:04,500
you don't have faith in me.

162
00:12:08,820 --> 00:12:10,220
Then who do you think

163
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:12,860
can obtain the 500 silver taels?

164
00:12:13,580 --> 00:12:14,500
Lord Bai, Xiao Chong?

165
00:12:15,460 --> 00:12:16,700
Lord Chi, Xiao Yu?

166
00:12:18,460 --> 00:12:21,340
I have faith in Lord Yong'an,

167
00:12:21,340 --> 00:12:22,620
Xiao Chuhe,

168
00:12:23,340 --> 00:12:25,700
not Xiao Se of the Snowfall Villa.

169
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:31,900
Are martial arts skills

170
00:12:32,820 --> 00:12:34,260
important to you?

171
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:35,260
You know

172
00:12:35,420 --> 00:12:36,580
that was not what I meant.

173
00:12:36,780 --> 00:12:38,540
Just look at yourself.

174
00:12:39,780 --> 00:12:40,580
What's wrong with me?

175
00:12:43,740 --> 00:12:48,300
You are arrogant, thin-skinned, and boastful.

176
00:12:48,660 --> 00:12:53,100
You show off your petty tricks,
treat others ruthlessly, and are self-righteous.

177
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:56,620
These are the six shortcomings
a monarch should avoid.

178
00:13:02,300 --> 00:13:02,900
Master,

179
00:13:03,700 --> 00:13:04,660
it's your turn.

180
00:13:07,020 --> 00:13:07,740
I'm passing it down to you.

181
00:13:09,180 --> 00:13:10,340
My martial arts skills are crippled.

182
00:13:10,340 --> 00:13:11,860
How is this Wuji Staff going to be useful to me?

183
00:13:15,460 --> 00:13:17,300
It's going to be a rough journey
to claim that 500 silver taels.

184
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:19,860
You can use it as a crutch.

185
00:13:27,020 --> 00:13:27,860
Thank you, Master.

186
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:32,900
Master,

187
00:13:33,700 --> 00:13:34,940
there's one thing I still can't figure out.

188
00:13:35,420 --> 00:13:36,460
I hope you can enlighten me.

189
00:13:37,060 --> 00:13:37,700
What is it?

190
00:13:38,540 --> 00:13:39,700
I want to go to Yushi.

191
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:40,980
Can you tell me the direction?

192
00:13:41,780 --> 00:13:42,900
Are you lost?

193
00:13:44,780 --> 00:13:45,460
Yes.

194
00:13:50,060 --> 00:13:50,700
Master,

195
00:13:51,260 --> 00:13:52,180
this is not funny.

196
00:13:52,580 --> 00:13:54,020
I thought

197
00:13:54,180 --> 00:13:55,620
you brought those two lads to their deaths

198
00:13:55,820 --> 00:13:56,980
on purpose.

199
00:13:57,660 --> 00:13:58,500
Seek death?

200
00:13:59,540 --> 00:14:01,060
There's a city

201
00:14:01,420 --> 00:14:02,740
30 li to the west.

202
00:14:03,860 --> 00:14:04,380
What city?

203
00:14:04,940 --> 00:14:05,820
Muliang City?

204
00:14:06,860 --> 00:14:07,660
Did I hear that correctly?

205
00:14:08,860 --> 00:14:09,540
I can't believe

206
00:14:10,580 --> 00:14:11,740
that we'd come here

207
00:14:13,020 --> 00:14:13,700
by accident.

208
00:14:16,700 --> 00:14:17,140
Xiao Se,

209
00:14:17,300 --> 00:14:18,020
why don't you give

210
00:14:18,180 --> 00:14:18,740
any reaction at all?

211
00:14:20,740 --> 00:14:21,980
What kind of reaction should I have?

212
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:24,700
There are four major cities in this world.

213
00:14:25,020 --> 00:14:26,460
Tianqi of the North, Xueyue of the South,

214
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:28,340
Wushuang of the East, and Muliang of the West.

215
00:14:28,580 --> 00:14:29,540
It's a city as famous as Xueyue City

216
00:14:29,700 --> 00:14:31,380
in the martial arts world.

217
00:14:31,540 --> 00:14:32,780
I must go and visit it.

218
00:14:34,940 --> 00:14:36,300
It's nothing but a deserted ghost city.

219
00:14:36,620 --> 00:14:37,780
What's so special about it?

220
00:14:38,140 --> 00:14:39,620
How can you say that?

221
00:14:40,260 --> 00:14:41,700
Every martial artist knows

222
00:14:42,140 --> 00:14:43,740
there is this one person living in Muliang City.

223
00:14:44,540 --> 00:14:45,940
And this is the person

224
00:14:46,180 --> 00:14:47,020
who made Muliang City

225
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:48,740
one of the four most famous cities.

226
00:14:51,820 --> 00:14:53,100
This person is one of the Five Sword Deities,

227
00:14:53,700 --> 00:14:55,260
Luo Qingyang, the Lone Sword Deity.

228
00:14:58,380 --> 00:14:59,180
The Lone Sword Deity,

229
00:15:00,820 --> 00:15:01,740
Luo Qingyang.

230
00:15:11,700 --> 00:15:12,300
Enough said.

231
00:15:13,180 --> 00:15:14,540
How would he not know

232
00:15:14,700 --> 00:15:16,290
about rumors in the martial arts world?

233
00:15:17,940 --> 00:15:20,340
It's said the Lone Sword Deity, Luo Qingyang,

234
00:15:20,860 --> 00:15:22,580
lives alone in Muliang City
to practice his swordsmanship.

235
00:15:23,060 --> 00:15:25,100
He has never left the city
for more than ten years.

236
00:15:25,900 --> 00:15:27,260
He claims he'll only leave the city

237
00:15:27,460 --> 00:15:28,220
after he masters

238
00:15:28,740 --> 00:15:29,700
the Nine-Song Sword Technique.

239
00:15:31,660 --> 00:15:32,250
His situation

240
00:15:32,250 --> 00:15:33,580
is quite similar

241
00:15:34,180 --> 00:15:34,860
to Lei Hong of the Lei Clan.

242
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:39,100
Lei Hong, Luo Qingyang,

243
00:15:39,780 --> 00:15:41,620
and Zhao Yuzhen,

244
00:15:42,100 --> 00:15:43,060
who has never left

245
00:15:43,180 --> 00:15:44,300
Mount Wangcheng

246
00:15:44,460 --> 00:15:45,220
since he was born.

247
00:15:45,860 --> 00:15:46,540
These three people

248
00:15:47,020 --> 00:15:48,420
are considered the three homebodies
in the martial arts world.

249
00:15:50,740 --> 00:15:51,500
Wait, why are you...

250
00:15:51,660 --> 00:15:52,820
But not many rumors in the martial arts world

251
00:15:52,860 --> 00:15:53,860
are true.

252
00:15:54,900 --> 00:15:56,100
Lei Hong and Zhao Yuzhen

253
00:15:56,260 --> 00:15:57,020
at least have the support of the Lei Clan

254
00:15:57,020 --> 00:15:58,180
and Mount Wangcheng respectively.

255
00:15:59,020 --> 00:15:59,940
But there's only Luo Qingyang

256
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:01,380
in Muliang City.

257
00:16:02,060 --> 00:16:03,420
What has he been eating and drinking

258
00:16:03,420 --> 00:16:04,100
for the past ten years?

259
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:06,180
Does he really think
his title makes him an immortal

260
00:16:06,420 --> 00:16:07,780
who doesn't eat or drink?

261
00:16:08,020 --> 00:16:10,060
You have a point.

262
00:16:10,220 --> 00:16:12,140
Rumors may be exaggerated.

263
00:16:12,660 --> 00:16:14,620
But the title of Luo Qingyang

264
00:16:15,140 --> 00:16:16,370
as the Sword Deity is real.

265
00:16:17,020 --> 00:16:17,900
Many people think

266
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:19,660
Luo Qingyang's martial arts skills

267
00:16:20,140 --> 00:16:21,660
can rank first among the Five Sword Deities.

268
00:16:24,780 --> 00:16:25,340
Lei Wujie.

269
00:16:26,580 --> 00:16:26,900
Lei Wujie!

270
00:16:28,140 --> 00:16:28,620
What's wrong?

271
00:16:30,300 --> 00:16:33,140
I mean,

272
00:16:33,860 --> 00:16:34,820
since we're already here,

273
00:16:35,140 --> 00:16:37,460
why don't we go and take a look?

274
00:16:38,380 --> 00:16:38,780
Shall we?

275
00:16:43,900 --> 00:16:44,500
Master Wuchan,

276
00:16:44,940 --> 00:16:45,460
how long

277
00:16:45,620 --> 00:16:46,380
until we reach Jiulong Sect?

278
00:16:46,820 --> 00:16:47,420
We're almost there.

279
00:16:57,340 --> 00:17:00,060
Lian, it's sweet.

280
00:17:02,740 --> 00:17:03,540
Here.

281
00:17:06,260 --> 00:17:07,820
Why aren't you eating?

282
00:17:09,660 --> 00:17:11,260
Let me feed you.

283
00:17:40,220 --> 00:17:41,140
Tang Lian, we'll...

