00:17:54,860 --> 00:17:56,420
Xiao Se's face turned pale

285
00:17:56,900 --> 00:17:58,420
when I said I was going

286
00:17:58,700 --> 00:18:00,260
to Muliang City.

287
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:02,060
Wuxin is the same too.

288
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:03,580
What did he mean

289
00:18:03,740 --> 00:18:04,700
