296
00:18:13,700 --> 00:18:14,420
He actually asked us to meet him

297
00:18:14,580 --> 00:18:15,460
at the Western Regions' border.

298
00:18:16,020 --> 00:18:17,140
The situation in Beili

299
00:18:17,340 --> 00:18:18,460
is different from Nanjue's.

300
00:18:19,820 --> 00:18:20,700
Their crown prince

301
00:18:20,860 --> 00:18:22,100
