00:18:26,140 --> 00:18:27,380
in the martial arts world in secret.

306
00:18:28,300 --> 00:18:29,580
Other than Lord Chi, Xiao Yu,

307
00:18:29,780 --> 00:18:31,100
there's Lord Bai, Xiao Chong.

308
00:18:33,620 --> 00:18:35,380
Behind Lord Bai, Xiao Chong,

309
00:18:36,060 --> 00:18:39,860
