00:18:55,860 --> 00:18:56,300
Who's there?

314
00:19:03,860 --> 00:19:04,460
Was that thunder?

315
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:07,620
But it doesn't look like it's going to rain.

316
00:19:09,820 --> 00:19:11,260
That's the direction Lei Wujie went.

317
00:19:12,260 --> 00:19:12,820
Could it be

318
00:19:13,780 --> 00:19:14,980
he's engaging in a fight with someone?

319
00:19:17,580 --> 00:19:18,460
This airhead

320
00:19:18,980 --> 00:19:20,740
could cause trouble from anything.

321
00:19:21,660 --> 00:19:23,020
This place is quite secluded.

322
00:19:24,260 --> 00:19:26,660
To my surprise, Lei Wujie would run into people

323
00:19:26,820 --> 00:19:28,300
who made him use his explosives.

324
00:19:34,220 --> 00:19:35,660
They're on the move.

325
00:19:36,300 --> 00:19:36,980
It looks like

326
00:19:37,860 --> 00:19:39,860
they're heading in the direction of Muliang City.

327
00:19:40,940 --> 00:19:41,700
Muliang City.

328
00:19:43,980 --> 00:19:44,980
Lone Sword Deity.

329
00:19:56,900 --> 00:19:57,580
What?

330
00:19:58,260 --> 00:19:58,980
Aren't you going to rescue him?

331
00:20:00,780 --> 00:20:01,340
No.

332
00:20:06,100 --> 00:20:06,740
What did you say?

333
00:20:08,700 --> 00:20:09,700
That airhead

334
00:20:09,740 --> 00:20:10,340
