336
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:13,540
He'll be back here soon.

337
00:20:15,420 --> 00:20:16,210
You may say that.

338
00:20:17,260 --> 00:20:17,900
But they're heading

339
00:20:17,900 --> 00:20:19,140
toward Muliang City.

340
00:20:20,180 --> 00:20:21,540
If they provoked the Lone Sword Deity...

341
00:20:21,660 --> 00:20:23,140
Didn't he want to see the Lone Sword Deity?

342
00:20:25,820 --> 00:20:26,740
If he met him,

343
00:20:27,700 --> 00:20:28,740
it would be just as he wanted.

344
00:20:31,180 --> 00:20:31,900
Are you troubled by something?

345
00:20:32,940 --> 00:20:34,420
Since you came back last night,

346
00:20:35,020 --> 00:20:36,300
you've been a little off.

347
00:20:41,260 --> 00:20:42,500
If you want to go, you can go alone.

348
00:20:43,740 --> 00:20:44,940
That airhead was the one who wanted to help you.

349
00:20:45,300 --> 00:20:46,020
I never agreed to do so.

350
00:20:48,900 --> 00:20:49,900
I can take this chance

351
00:20:50,020 --> 00:20:50,740
to split ways with you.

352
00:20:50,940 --> 00:20:52,260
It's better for me this way.

353
00:21:00,300 --> 00:21:00,900
Are you

354
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:02,260
scared?

355
00:21:07,260 --> 00:21:08,220
You can go alone.

356
00:21:08,980 --> 00:21:09,500
Why do you want to take someone

357
00:21:09,700 --> 00:21:10,780
who doesn't know martial arts at all?

358
00:21:11,780 --> 00:21:13,180
Isn't Lei Wujie your companion?

359
00:21:15,740 --> 00:21:16,740
We only met by chance

360
00:21:16,820 --> 00:21:17,860
and became acquainted, that's all.

361
00:21:18,340 --> 00:21:19,980
His life

362
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:20,740
doesn't concern me.

363
00:21:24,180 --> 00:21:26,180
I've been smart since I was a child.

364
00:21:27,460 --> 00:21:28,860
I reached

365
00:21:29,020 --> 00:21:29,940
the Carefree Phase when I was 13.

366
00:21:30,700 --> 00:21:31,540
I was excited at the time

367
00:21:32,410 --> 00:21:33,500
and asked Old Wangyou

368
00:21:34,340 --> 00:21:34,940
if I was considered

369
00:21:34,940 --> 00:21:36,900
a prodigy of the generation.

370
00:21:39,180 --> 00:21:40,740
After I pestered him relentlessly,

371
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:42,300
he finally told me

372
00:21:43,180 --> 00:21:44,260
there was also someone in Beili

373
00:21:45,620 --> 00:21:47,020
who reached the Carefree Phase

374
00:21:47,300 --> 00:21:48,460
at 13.

375
00:21:48,740 --> 00:21:51,060
At 17, he reached the Insouciant Phase.

376
00:21:52,580 --> 00:21:53,260
He deserves the reputation

377
00:21:53,260 --> 00:21:54,820
of the greatest prodigy in the world.

378
00:21:56,260 --> 00:21:56,940
He's the disciple

379
00:21:57,420 --> 00:21:58,980
of Polymath of the martial arts world,

380
00:21:59,780 --> 00:22:01,100
the Sixth Prince of Beili,

381
00:22:01,660 --> 00:22:02,780
Xiao Chuhe.

382
00:22:04,060 --> 00:22:04,700
Soon after that,

383
00:22:05,100 --> 00:22:06,460
the incident with Lord Langya happened.

384
00:22:08,300 --> 00:22:09,260
Li Xinyue, one of the Four Guardians of Tianqi,

385
00:22:09,460 --> 00:22:10,660
had died.

386
00:22:12,460 --> 00:22:13,780
(Her daughter, Li Hanyi,)

387
00:22:14,580 --> 00:22:15,980
(pointed her sword at the Emperor,)

388
00:22:17,020 --> 00:22:17,820
(which shook the martial arts world.)

389
00:22:19,060 --> 00:22:21,500
(It's said Xiao Chuhe kneeled in Tianqi City)

390
00:22:21,540 --> 00:22:22,980
(for three days and three nights)

391
00:22:23,740 --> 00:22:25,180
(to plead mercy for Lord Langya.)

392
00:22:25,500 --> 00:22:27,940
(Finally, he was implicated)

393
00:22:28,340 --> 00:22:29,220
(and demoted to a commoner.)

394
00:22:30,060 --> 00:22:31,020
At that time, I thought

395
00:22:31,980 --> 00:22:32,980
Xiao Chuhe

396
00:22:33,540 --> 00:22:34,700
may be from the imperial family.

397
00:22:35,780 --> 00:22:36,700
But he's unexpectedly

398
00:22:36,940 --> 00:22:37,820
to be a righteous person.

399
00:22:39,020 --> 00:22:40,660
It's someone worth making friends with.

400
00:22:41,540 --> 00:22:42,460
At first,

401
00:22:44,020 --> 00:22:45,260
I thought you were Xiao Chuhe.

402
00:22:53,020 --> 00:22:53,980
Stop pretending

403
00:22:54,100 --> 00:22:55,700
as if you know everything.

404
00:22:56,980 --> 00:22:58,500
You like telling stories, right?

405
00:22:58,780 --> 00:23:00,180
I can tell you one too.

406
00:23:01,340 --> 00:23:02,900
In the last battle
of the Demon Sect's expedition in the east

407
00:23:03,020 --> 00:23:03,620
12 years ago,

408
00:23:05,780 --> 00:23:06,700
every major sect in Beili

409
00:23:07,180 --> 00:23:09,100
besieged the Head of the Demon Sect, Ye Dingzhi.

410
00:23:10,180 --> 00:23:11,740
Ye Dingzhi was defeated

411
00:23:11,940 --> 00:23:12,860
and died after he took his own life.

412
00:23:15,380 --> 00:23:16,260
The funny thing

413
00:23:16,780 --> 00:23:18,260
was the person who betrayed Ye Dingzhi

414
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:20,380
was his best friend,

415
00:23:20,620 --> 00:23:21,340
Wang Rensun.

416
00:23:22,100 --> 00:23:23,140
In my opinion,

417
00:23:23,860 --> 00:23:24,700
Ye Dingzhi claimed himself

418
00:23:24,860 --> 00:23:26,380
to be the greatest in the world.

419
00:23:26,660 --> 00:23:28,660
But he eventually died
because of his friend's betrayal.

420
00:23:29,540 --> 00:23:30,820
Utmost stupidity.

421
00:23:36,620 --> 00:23:38,500
Why? Does that humiliate you?

422
00:23:39,020 --> 00:23:40,100
Without using any martial arts skills,

423
00:23:40,980 --> 00:23:42,020
I'm going to teach you a lesson.

424
00:23:42,140 --> 00:23:42,940
I'm warning you.

425
00:23:45,300 --> 00:23:45,540
Are you mad?

426
00:23:45,740 --> 00:23:46,820
I'm going to rip your foul mouth!

427
00:23:54,100 --> 00:23:54,500
Are you out of your mind?

428
00:24:02,180 --> 00:24:04,980
(You are arrogant, thin-skinned,)

429
00:24:05,220 --> 00:24:08,180
(and boastful. You show off your petty tricks,)

430
00:24:08,660 --> 00:24:11,260
(treat others ruthlessly, and are self-righteous.)

431
00:24:11,740 --> 00:24:14,740
(These are the six shortcomings
a monarch should avoid.)

432
00:24:27,780 --> 00:24:28,500
I'm sorry.

433
00:24:30,060 --> 00:24:30,580
Today,

434
00:24:31,780 --> 00:24:32,780
there's no Young Head

435
00:24:32,780 --> 00:24:33,700
of Tianwaitian

436
00:24:34,780 --> 00:24:36,420
or Xiao Chuhe.

437
00:24:37,780 --> 00:24:39,300
I'm only Wuxin from Hanshui Temple.

438
00:24:51,620 --> 00:24:52,420
No matter what,

439
00:24:53,780 --> 00:24:54,420
Lei Wujie came here

440
00:24:54,620 --> 00:24:55,420
because of me.

441
00:24:56,740 --> 00:24:57,860
So I must go and bring him back.

442
00:25:10,300 --> 00:25:10,780
(And you)

443
00:25:12,180 --> 00:25:14,100
(are only Xiao Se of Snowfall Villa.)

444
00:25:15,180 --> 00:25:17,620
(I have faith in Lord Yong'an,)

445
00:25:17,780 --> 00:25:19,020
(Xiao Chuhe,)

446
00:25:19,940 --> 00:25:22,180
(not Xiao Se of the Snowfall Villa.)

447
00:25:23,820 --> 00:25:25,220
I dare you to fight one on one.

448
00:25:25,540 --> 00:25:26,900
Do you call yourself great for outnumbering me?

449
00:25:27,180 --> 00:25:28,700
Rascal, cut the crap.

450
00:25:29,020 --> 00:25:30,300
Who sent you here?

451
00:25:34,820 --> 00:25:35,700
Just kill me if you want.

452
00:25:36,140 --> 00:25:37,180
If I blink,

453
00:25:37,340 --> 00:25:38,100
I'm not a hero!

454
00:25:38,820 --> 00:25:40,340
(These people seem)

455
00:25:40,540 --> 00:25:42,580
-(to be carrying Nanjue's long blade.)
-Untie me now!

456
00:25:43,540 --> 00:25:45,100
-(This man does look familiar.)
-We can fight until the day turns dark.

457
00:25:45,540 --> 00:25:46,940
(He's the Crown Prince of Nanjue's guard,)

458
00:25:47,500 --> 00:25:48,380
(Fu Hengxing.)

459
00:25:49,300 --> 00:25:50,260
(There must be a special reason)

460
00:25:50,260 --> 00:25:51,460
(for him to show up here.)

461
00:25:51,700 --> 00:25:53,020
(I think Wujie must have
overheard their conversation)

462
00:25:53,180 --> 00:25:53,780
(by accident.)

463
00:25:55,660 --> 00:25:57,020
(Why is Wuxin not here yet?)

464
00:25:57,940 --> 00:25:59,140
Teach him a lesson.

465
00:25:59,660 --> 00:26:00,580
You're not serious, are you?

466
00:26:01,060 --> 00:26:01,740
No!

467
00:26:06,620 --> 00:26:07,180
Stop!

468
00:26:10,660 --> 00:26:11,140
Xiao Se!

469
00:26:17,180 --> 00:26:17,940
You?

470
00:26:19,140 --> 00:26:20,380
I didn't expect you to remember me.

471
00:26:21,300 --> 00:26:22,260
How could I forget?

472
00:26:22,860 --> 00:26:23,980
The Crown Prince

473
00:26:23,980 --> 00:26:25,140
is still upset

474
00:26:25,580 --> 00:26:27,580
about losing a city to you

475
00:26:28,140 --> 00:26:30,140
at the Qianjin Gambling House
in Tianqi City back then.

476
00:26:31,660 --> 00:26:33,260
That was the folly of youth.

477
00:26:34,380 --> 00:26:35,620
Since you showed up here,

478
00:26:36,140 --> 00:26:37,020
I suppose you know

479
00:26:37,180 --> 00:26:38,340
a lot about us.

480
00:26:49,580 --> 00:26:51,300
How's my worthless brother

481
00:26:51,780 --> 00:26:52,700
doing now?

482
00:26:55,700 --> 00:26:57,140
It looks like you know everything.

483
00:26:57,700 --> 00:26:59,100
That's why you brought him to stop us.

484
00:26:59,740 --> 00:27:01,620
What a clever strategy.

485
00:27:01,700 --> 00:27:03,380
It's not my clever strategy.

486
00:27:04,140 --> 00:27:05,860
After all, nothing in Beili

487
00:27:06,060 --> 00:27:07,780
goes unnoticed by that person.

488
00:27:07,940 --> 00:27:08,700
Are you here under orders?

489
00:27:09,220 --> 00:27:10,380
I'm only here to deliver a message.

490
00:27:10,740 --> 00:27:11,540
I hope you can go back

491
00:27:11,660 --> 00:27:12,780
and tell your crown prince

492
00:27:13,540 --> 00:27:15,420
that there are some things he can't meddle with.

493
00:27:21,220 --> 00:27:23,260
I was almost tricked by you.

494
00:27:24,060 --> 00:27:25,020
Why do you say so?

495
00:27:25,580 --> 00:27:26,540
As far as I know,

496
00:27:28,140 --> 00:27:30,900
you were banished from Tianqi City.

497
00:27:34,860 --> 00:27:36,260
That information is right.

498
00:27:37,100 --> 00:27:38,300
But matters in Tianqi City

499
00:27:39,220 --> 00:27:40,780
are more unfathomable than you imagined.

500
00:27:41,820 --> 00:27:42,460
If you don't believe me,

501
00:27:43,980 --> 00:27:44,700
you can try.

502
00:27:45,780 --> 00:27:46,420
All right.

503
00:27:48,100 --> 00:27:49,540
I'm willing to try.

504
00:27:53,860 --> 00:27:55,580
Why aren't you fighting?
Do you only know how to avoid my attacks?

505
00:28:03,900 --> 00:28:04,740
I didn't expect

506
00:28:04,940 --> 00:28:06,100
the prodigy of the world in the past

507
00:28:06,820 --> 00:28:08,620
can't even hold his own weapon.

508
00:28:09,180 --> 00:28:10,380
How tragic.

509
00:28:11,380 --> 00:28:11,980
Prepare to die!

510
00:28:12,580 --> 00:28:12,980
Xiao Se!

511
00:28:22,740 --> 00:28:23,060
Wuxin.

512
00:28:24,020 --> 00:28:24,860
Leave now.

513
00:28:27,020 --> 00:28:27,820
Let's go.

514
00:28:28,900 --> 00:28:29,860
When did you arrive?

515
00:28:32,090 --> 00:28:32,980
It was when you started

516
00:28:33,140 --> 00:28:34,020
confronting that person.

517
00:28:34,580 --> 00:28:35,460
Since you were already here,

518
00:28:35,780 --> 00:28:37,100
why didn't you make a move earlier?

519
00:28:38,500 --> 00:28:39,620
I wanted to,

520
00:28:40,540 --> 00:28:41,420
but you were talking

521
00:28:41,660 --> 00:28:42,620
about the folly of youth.

522
00:28:43,060 --> 00:28:43,660
I found it interesting,

523
00:28:44,220 --> 00:28:45,220
so I decided to watch it longer.

524
00:28:47,260 --> 00:28:47,620
Then,

525
00:28:47,780 --> 00:28:48,780
can you untie me?

526
00:28:59,020 --> 00:28:59,340
Xiao Se,

527
00:28:59,900 --> 00:29:01,540
you know that person?

528
00:29:01,900 --> 00:29:02,780
As I listen to you talking,

529
00:29:03,140 --> 00:29:04,300
I find it so confusing.

530
00:29:04,540 --> 00:29:04,980
I don't completely understand.

531
00:29:05,580 --> 00:29:06,620
From what he said,

532
00:29:06,860 --> 00:29:07,940
you used to be an official

533
00:29:08,100 --> 00:29:08,740
in Tianqi City.

534
00:29:09,260 --> 00:29:10,260
But you were dismissed after that.

535
00:29:10,420 --> 00:29:10,780
Why?

536
00:29:11,540 --> 00:29:12,780
You also mentioned your brother.

537
00:29:13,340 --> 00:29:14,220
What's going on?

538
00:29:15,460 --> 00:29:16,420
Say something.

539
00:29:18,380 --> 00:29:19,220
You obviously

540
00:29:19,420 --> 00:29:20,300
can kill those three.

541
00:29:20,660 --> 00:29:21,340
Why didn't you do it?

542
00:29:23,580 --> 00:29:24,940
How can I take lives as I please?

543
00:29:26,940 --> 00:29:28,100
If they find out they were tricked,

544
00:29:28,260 --> 00:29:29,060
they'll definitely come back for us.

545
00:29:29,740 --> 00:29:30,660
We should get out of here now.

546
00:29:31,660 --> 00:29:32,140
You're right.

547
00:29:33,340 --> 00:29:34,660
We should hit the road to Yushi Kingdom.

548
00:29:37,860 --> 00:29:38,620
You didn't even

549
00:29:38,780 --> 00:29:39,540
answer my questions.

550
00:29:41,260 --> 00:29:42,980
Xiao Se, why?

551
00:29:43,140 --> 00:29:47,940
[Dafanyin Temple]

552
00:29:51,900 --> 00:29:52,380
Lingjun,

553
00:29:53,100 --> 00:29:53,900
where is he now?

554
00:29:55,500 --> 00:29:57,100
Master, the scouts reported

555
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:58,300
that he escaped

556
00:29:58,740 --> 00:29:59,900
from Belle's Manor several days ago.

557
00:30:00,420 --> 00:30:01,180
During his escape, he ran into

558
00:30:01,380 --> 00:30:02,180
the Western Regions'
most vicious mounted bandits.

559
00:30:03,420 --> 00:30:04,620
After that, he created chaos

560
00:30:05,300 --> 00:30:06,060
and is nowhere to be found now.

561
00:30:07,300 --> 00:30:07,900
He should be

562
00:30:08,060 --> 00:30:08,900
on his way here.

563
00:30:10,100 --> 00:30:10,580
But...

564
00:30:12,060 --> 00:30:12,660
Keep talking.

565
00:30:13,460 --> 00:30:14,300
